Introduction

  • In this LAB we have conducted data visualization on the data which consists of different Signal Strength and ASU's reading taken at various places within BIAS campus and througout the Bhimtal Lake
  • The devices used were different models of phones such as Samsung, Vivo etc, and the sim used were Airtel, JIO and VI for the devices
  • First we import the CSV's files containing data within BIAS campus.
  • Then we installed the following libraries :
    1. matplotlib and seaborn to visualize our data
    2. pandas to clean and process data
  • After that we do some data cleaning using pandas , for eg:
    1. Renaming the coloumn name so that we can process them.
    2. Removing the decimal values so that we can plot graph out of them .
    3. Removing NaN and Null values to remove discrepancy.
  • After that We have performed the data visualization.

Procedure

N=df.shape[0]
a = 0
while N!=0:
  if pd.isnull(df.at[a, 'Names']) == True:
    df.at[a, 'Names'] = df.at[a-1, 'Names']
  if pd.isnull(df.at[a, 'Roll No.']) == True:
    df.at[a, 'Roll No.'] = df.at[a-1, 'Roll No.']

  N=N-1
  a=a+1

for index, row in average_ASU_CLASS.iterrows():
    plt.text(row['Location Name'], row['asu1'], f'Avg: {row["asu1"]:.2f}', ha='left', va='bottom')

for index, row in average_ASU_OUR.iterrows():
    plt.text(row['Location Name'], row['asu1'], f'Avg: {row["asu1"]:.2f}', ha='left', va='bottom')

# Adding labels and title
plt.xlabel('Location')
plt.ylabel('ASU')
plt.title('Comparison of ASU and Average ASU for class Data and our Data')

# Adding a legend
plt.legend()

# Show the plot
plt.grid(True)
plt.show()

Conclusion

BIAS Campus has enough 4G and 5G Signal band reach, the signals were never too low, and the spots with government office and tourist point of interests had the maximum strength recorded. Inside the campus, the New building has the best signal average. The signal distribution was very uniform except a few points of lacking. Overall the result was a satisfactory distributed of Bandwidth, for both low end and mid range smartphone processor modem to recieve for different sim Users.
